name: 臉內翻及瞼外翻
content: 臉內翻及瞼外翻 ECTROPION 黄斑點 (Macula) 眼角膜(Cornea) 晶體(Lens) 光線 light) 瞳孔 (Pupil) 瑪麗醫院 Queen Mary Hospital Introduction Eyelid ectropion is the outward rotation of the lid/lashes causing exposure of the conjunctiva and sometimes inability to close the eyes completely. When someone is suffering from ectropion the skin of the eyelid turns away from the eye. This will expose the bulbar conjunctiva leading to excessive tearing mucous discharge as well as crusting of the eyelid and an uncomfortable feeling. This condition may also affect the vision. 前房 (Anterior Chamber) 玻璃體 (Vitreous) 視神經 (Optic Nerve) 虹膜 Iris) 視網膜 (Retina) 眼球縱切面圖 論會局(港島區)眼科服務會介 Causes Ectropion usually occurs when the eyelid tissue becomes weak as a result of aging. However it can also result from eyelid scaring chemical/thermal injury of lid or facial nerve palsy. 進入廿一世紀整個港島區的眼科服務進行了整 合透過瑪麗醫院眼科部門的協作提升眼科臨床醫護 的水平及效率為港島市民提供優質現代化眼科醫療服 務 。 Treatment To prevent damage to the eye surgical repair is recommended. This is usually performed on an outpatient basis under local anesthesia. One can resume work within 2-3 days after surgery. Usually the wound will heal in 7 to 10 days. 我們各醫院的眼科專業人員包括眼科醫生、護 士、視光師及視覺矯正師等等組成一支強大的眼科專 業醫療隊伍為市民提供全面的眼科服務。此外我們 亦負責策劃和推行區內眼科服務的長遠發展並培訓眼 科醫護專職人員提升市民的健康質素。 院內翻及院外翻 ENTROPION AND ECTROPION Should you have any queries please consult your doctor during follow-up 瑪麗醫院 Queen Mary Hospital Tel: 2255 3111 QMH/EYE-19 01/2010 ENTROPION AND ECTROPION ENTROPION 院内翻及晚外翻 院内翻 簡介 驗內翻是眼瞼緣部位置異常朝向眼球倒 卷曲。卷曲的眼臉緣及睫毛會刺激眼球結 膜或角膜令眼刺痛流淚及結膜充血甚 至影響視力。 做外 簡介 驗外翻是臉緣向外翻轉離開附著的眼 球致驗結膜暴露在外有時會有臉裂 眼睛不能完全閉合。由於眼瞼外翻裏面 的組織如眼球結膜、眼瞼結膜甚至角膜 都得不到保護而乾燥。若角膜發炎會影響 視力。 Introduction Eyelid entropion is the inward rotation of eyelid/lash towards the eye. When someone is suffering from entropion the lashes of the eyelid and lid margin rub against the eye leading to excessive tearing mucous discharge redness and pain or discomfort. This condition may also affect the vision. 成因 成因 老年人由於皮膚失去正常張力皮下組 織鬆弛驗板下緣的肌肉向前方滑動 壓迫驗板致臉緣上部向內翻卷 是由於眼瞼肌肉或內內外險韌帶鬆弛、面神 經麻痹、創傷或手術後之疤痕造成。 Causes Entropion occurs when the eyelid tissue becomes weak as a result of aging. However it can also be due to scarring secondary to burn chemical injury trachoma cicatricial pemphigoid etc. C其他常見的驗內翻見於驗結膜或驗板慢 性炎症結膜疤痕收縮或是慢性砂眼 後遺症等 治療 需要做手術矯正。手術只需在局部麻醉下 進行不需住院。病人要簽署同意書。手 術後約二至三日後可恢復工作。七至十日 後傷口可以癒合。 治療 Treatment Surgery is recommended to repair entropion. This is achieved when the surgeon tightens the eyelid and its adjacent muscles. This is usually performed on an outpatient basis under local anesthesia. A written consent is required. 需要做手術矯正。將眼驗及其皮下組織拉 緊。手術只需在局部麻醉下進行不需住 院。病人要簽署同意書。 如有其他疑問可於覆診時向醫 生查詢
